Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:15.36,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:16.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.73,0:00:19.58,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you don't have \Nto hammer it{\i1} that{\i0} hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.03,0:00:22.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't really need to be \Nfixed in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:22.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:27.71,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:27.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought, this way, \Nit'll never fall off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.41,0:00:30.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. Never again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.76,0:00:33.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:35.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you already packed \Nand ready to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.61,0:00:36.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:37.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you're taking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.77,0:00:40.72,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.00,0:00:47.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.56,0:00:52.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings have become much \Nstronger than they were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.23,0:00:56.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My desire to become a voice actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:57.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:59.91,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Go home to Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:02.67,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:02.67,Saku-overlap,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mind if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:07.08,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Go convince your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:08.40,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.40,0:01:09.86,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that you've been getting by on \Nyour own these last two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.35,0:01:15.92,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking your own thoughts, \Nmaking your own decisions...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:18.56,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If you think that makes you an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:20.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you couldn't be more wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:24.12,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you do if you're \Na kid who can't be bothered...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:25.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to listen to others' opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sensei. You're being too harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:30.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Kanda-kun. She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.32,0:01:34.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,When my father opposed my decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.03,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I chose the easy way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.73,0:01:41.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I just threw a tantrum because I \Ndidn't get my way, and ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:45.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go home and talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.31,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them to let me pursue my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:50.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask them to let me stay in Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.19,0:01:52.17,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:56.93,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.08,0:02:01.01,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your last two years weren't a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:03.11,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:13.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how she acts, she does \Nsound like a teacher sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:17.86,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I rented a van!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.28,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Load 'er up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:23.47,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.06,0:02:24.98,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:25.96,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.64,0:02:26.37,Saku-overlap,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,So heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:30.17,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:34.28,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If you invite me to your \Nwedding, I'll come running.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.28,0:02:35.88,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're an infuriating brat to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.63,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.75,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.84,0:02:42.65,Saku-overlap,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.65,0:02:43.46,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:53.91,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.39,0:02:56.19,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Am I late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:57.79,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.90,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,As a former resident of Sakura Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:04.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see off my successors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.24,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:07.24,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:11.08,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I'd come fill \Nthe hole in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.66,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:16.88,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to go for drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:18.34,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,What? This early?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:19.75,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.35,0:03:25.79,Saku-main,KAZUKI,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:10.41,Saku-main,SONG,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's be friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:17.12,Saku-main,SONG,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Goodbye for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:22.68,Saku-main,SONG,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Until we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.68,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.73,Saku-main,SONG,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Until we meet again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:31.31,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,First, Rita...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:33.56,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know when we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:38.14,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke, please don't forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:42.07,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,How am I supposed to forget you when \Nyou're constantly coming to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.39,0:05:43.64,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:46.78,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ryunosuke, it's time for \Nour touching farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:48.36,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing something \Ninappropriate again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:50.72,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,What's so inappropriate \Nabout a handshake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:52.70,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a handshake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.59,0:05:54.41,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.13,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.57,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Rita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.81,0:06:04.05,Saku-main,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,You're as gullible as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:09.01,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-H-How shameless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:11.26,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of behavior is—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:10.80,Saku-overlap,RITA,0000,0000,0000,,And one for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaaait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.63,0:06:16.11,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Jin-san and Aoyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.98,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:22.94,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand being away \Nfrom you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.15,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I feel anxious when you're not around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.86,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that untrustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.18,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I just wish I had \Nsomething more certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:34.16,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.93,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll take a \Npage out of Rita-san's book.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:41.75,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're demons...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:46.42,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,If that's still not enough, \NI'll leave you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.97,Sign,LETTER,0000,0000,0000,,To Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.97,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a love letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.48,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,C-Congratulations on getting hitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.80,0:07:02.12,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,That's not funny, Aoyama-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:04.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's the form from...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:11.03,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Once I get back from Osaka, \Nlet's go submit it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:12.53,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.17,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:15.69,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.84,0:07:19.30,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:20.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:21.33,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:23.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.45,0:07:25.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, get home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.32,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,No, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.32,0:07:27.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:31.22,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami's home is Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's right. Come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.32,0:07:38.50,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:47.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give up. I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:52.44,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.49,0:08:04.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Let's be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.63,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we don't have enough people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The van feels kinda empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.64,0:08:12.48,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,And finally,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.76,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.64,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Mashiron.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:21.14,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to Suimei University, \Nso we'll see each other soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.22,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I've got to go home \Nand prepare for the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:24.94,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.18,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Sakura Hall for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.18,0:08:30.14,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Akasaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:37.98,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make a game by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.57,0:08:43.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Watching Misaki-senpai made me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:45.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should make something \Njust because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:50.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like me could start \Nworking on something by myself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:54.08,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Given your current programming abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.26,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,you're limited in what you can produce.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:08:59.15,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,However, it's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:02.10,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,You could use a free game engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.59,0:09:05.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's all I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:08.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Since I made it through my presentation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.20,0:09:09.93,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like a door has opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:11.91,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But I learned that there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:14.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,an unbelievably large world \Nwaiting on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:18.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It may be frightening, \Nbut I have to start walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.58,0:09:25.76,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:29.11,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a meeting. I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,A meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:33.51,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought you did all \Nyour work through email.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:42.56,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Once in a blue moon, I have work \Nto do outside my room, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:49.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the two of us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:51.23,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:53.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.74,0:09:55.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The cherry blossoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been a year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:38.22,Saku-main,WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,Two coffees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:38.90,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.39,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You could use one, right, Aoyama-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:43.62,Saku-main,AOYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.80,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Are you nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:52.24,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's been a while since \NI last saw my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:55.34,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I think you've made the right decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.23,0:10:57.76,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,We're just getting started.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.67,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for us to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:02.93,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Not on Sorata, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.23,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:06.82,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.82,0:11:07.98,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,How grown-up of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:10.32,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,So bitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.03,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The first night I moved into Sakura Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:32.41,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I looked in each of the empty rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:35.46,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,and I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:38.17,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,My dream was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.54,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,for all of Sakura Hall's \Nrooms to be filled,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:46.68,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and for days full of warm light \Nand laughter to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.03,0:11:56.84,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:02.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to hang it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. You should've told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a fabrication.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari would never let you hold her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.25,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She does sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:20.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:21.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:24.12,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hikari let you kiss her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:28.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,They were kissing all \Nover the place earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:32.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean Senpai and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You make them sound like perverts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try kissing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:49.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:50.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:55.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Is it... necessary for the \Nmanga you're drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:59.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided yet, but probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:00.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:10.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:20.90,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'd appreciate it if \Nyou'd close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:45.39,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari's jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.39,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:49.96,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:51.83,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.87,0:13:55.31,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's interesting because there's \Nsomething to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:58.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.83,0:14:11.16,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,My reservation for the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.70,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:34.29,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Our futures will go on for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:48.90,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,30th Suimei University High School \Nof the Arts Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:48.90,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,What? Sakura Hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.12,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Hase-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:54.01,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,The regular dorms have shared rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:56.39,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep in the presence of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.03,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, my roommate \Nmade a real racket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:00.75,Saku-main,STUDENTS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:03.53,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I need to take care of \Nthe procedures to move in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:06.30,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Faculty Office
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.59,0:15:06.62,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.01,Sign,CARD,0000,0000,0000,,Hase Kanna
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.01,Sign,CARD,0000,0000,0000,,General Education Curriculum: Class 1-1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:09.01,Sign,CARD,0000,0000,0000,,Kamakura Wada Public High School Graduate
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:09.01,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so you're the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.30,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.85,0:15:15.08,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,This is the highest-scoring \Nfreshman, Hase Kanna-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.22,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the student exiled \Nfrom the regular dorms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.22,0:15:21.41,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,for sneaking a peek in the girls' \Nbathroom, Himemiya Iori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:22.55,Saku-main,KANNA,0000,0000,0000,,A Peeping Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:26.10,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister would cry if she knew \Nher younger brother had become...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.44,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,a criminal immediately \Nafter starting school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:29.63,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Don't spread such scandalous \Nrumors about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:31.14,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't actually see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.14,Saku-overlap,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:35.69,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you'll be able to \Nhave a normal high school life,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:39.10,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but welcome to Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:42.60,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I brought you this from Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That sauce looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:47.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We can turn half of this \Ninto tuna cutlets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:48.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,When I said I was throwing a \Nparty for the new students,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.54,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the fishmonger gave it to me for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.87,0:15:55.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We can make hotpot with the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:59.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to welcome them to \NSakura Hall with hotpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.06,0:16:00.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Just like they did for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.88,0:16:03.50,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're really acting \Nlike an upperclassman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.53,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, nothing. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:09.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You just got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.70,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go unpack your luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:13.14,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:19.66,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Duty Board{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:19.66,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda: Mashiro Duty\NShiina\NAkasaka\NAoyama
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:16.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's great your dad accepted your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.66,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure he accepted it. \NI kinda forced it on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:23.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But I think he realized I \Nwas serious about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.38,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Not going home for two years \Nreally made an impression.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.06,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I plan to work part-time again\N this year and save up money...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:34.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can attend a different training school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:38.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So, we'll get to work hard together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:39.15,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.10,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}Horror Adventure{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:43.10,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Western House of the Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.42,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your new pitch proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.10,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:47.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Aoyama, could you \Nhelp me out with it later?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:48.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.68,0:16:50.09,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's a horror adventure game...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.57,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that takes place in a \NWestern-style house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:56.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping to make a prototype \Nfor the title screening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.00,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you do some voices for...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're assuming that your \Npresentation will be successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:04.21,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm getting ahead of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.51,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that you're more confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.92,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There are some lines here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:11.52,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:13.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you standing so far away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.25,Saku-main,KANNA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near a pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.26,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.29,0:17:19.43,Saku-main,KANNA,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.15,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Blood! I want blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:32.11,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Young blood! Give me \Nyour fresh, dripping blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:33.61,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:38.66,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:47.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:17:58.63,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,A total hottie...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:01.29,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,And a pigsty of a room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.24,0:18:03.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A new person?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:04.48,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:07.47,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Himemiya Iori, and I'm going \Nto be living here starting—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.15,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.82,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.53,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:13.22,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:17.36,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Got it! If that's what you want,\N I'm more than happy to oblige!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:19.49,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro, the new students...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.90,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What do you think \Nyou're doing, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:26.15,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what it looks like! I—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.15,0:18:27.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A painting of the new people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:34.59,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to add the new \Nstudents to this painting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:39.83,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The skeletal structures of men are \Nvaried and difficult to paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.97,0:18:43.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we scared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.47,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to cut the grass, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.89,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.89,0:18:51.13,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the new students into the \Nnicest possible environment?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:55.63,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's fine. I enjoy a little excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:56.50,Saku-main,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She's still in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:58.95,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat without her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:04.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.85,0:19:06.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.65,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I was even at the Suimei \N High entrance ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:12.25,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Until yesterday, I was \NKanna-chan's roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:16.43,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to surprise you, so I \Nasked Mom and Dad not to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:18.28,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember my exam number?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It was 99, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.00,0:19:23.37,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,But! It was a fake number \Nmeant to deceive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:26.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell me it was actually \N66, I'm cutting ties with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:27.33,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.52,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.28,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:32.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to acknowledge \Nwe're related by blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:35.02,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.97,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:40.03,Saku-main,KANNA,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. In such a short amount of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.26,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,You left me out, Mashiro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:43.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.25,Saku-main,YUKO,0000,0000,0000,,Make me a member of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:48.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I respectfully decline your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.75,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,There's no space to paint Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.96,Saku-main,SoRATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yuko, we're going to talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:20:01.24,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I moved in next door. \NI came over to pay my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.46,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming. Hold your—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:03.91,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:07.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the newlywed who moved \Nin next door, Mitaka Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:08.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Mitaka Misaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:10.46,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.77,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka Jin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.77,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Mitaka Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.42,0:20:13.77,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't wait until Jin graduated,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:16.48,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,so I submitted the marriage registration.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:17.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:19.37,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like hotpot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.55,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You can save the moving soba for later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:22.46,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiigusa-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.26,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,Her tits are huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:25.73,Saku-main,IYORI,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:26.64,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What was that graduation \Nceremony speech about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:35.50,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall still has a variety of colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:40.04,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Colors from before, as well as new colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:42.39,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We each have...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:45.51,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,our own color shining brightly \Non the canvas of Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.24,0:20:50.64,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to leave this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:52.77,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided what I \Nwant to do in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:54.90,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,but for now, I guess I'm iridescent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:56.38,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will take off your underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.48,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.05,Saku-thought,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,He will send you a virus, lol!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.52,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Kouhai-kun, you're on Mashiro Duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.78,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I drew pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.95,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.57,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,is that it unconsciously \Nwraps up and destroys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:10.83,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.83,0:21:14.00,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Your scripts don't excite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.83,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up to you someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:19.38,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:24.17,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I think I wanted you to prove \Nhard work is rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.68,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to work hard with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:28.54,Saku-thought,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.54,0:21:30.49,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you not to work so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:36.04,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.19,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:40.52,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,love?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:44.67,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I love people who have goals!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.67,0:21:46.89,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I love people who work \Nas hard as they can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:48.85,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:52.75,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:55.73,Saku-thought,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Love is simply a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.73,0:21:57.22,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.22,0:21:58.92,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,So don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:02.28,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's not easy for me to tell \NMisaki how I feel about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.28,0:22:05.34,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is pounding \Nbecause you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:06.63,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your pulse sped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:08.29,Saku-thought,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Leap into space!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.35,0:22:11.93,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. I'm starting to have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:14.22,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stop running, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.22,0:22:16.27,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,All-out dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.99,0:22:21.86,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I don't know \Nwhat this feeling is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:23.73,Saku-thought,AKASAKA,0000,0000,0000,,Are your precious friendships so fragile...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.73,0:22:28.07,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,that you'd lose them just \Nbecause a building is torn down?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:29.62,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, they're not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:32.41,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be prepared \Nto be with her forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:34.41,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:37.63,Saku-thought,AOYAMA,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why am I not good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:47.74,Saku-thought,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1000)}My chest hurts, kouhai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:54.92,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall is Sakura Hall \Nbecause everyone is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.53,0:22:56.88,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We're all Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.79,0:23:00.84,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,How far do you think we can go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.80,0:23:03.76,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We can go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:07.61,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I feel, living \Nat Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:17.23,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.28,0:23:25.39,Saku-thought,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What color do you want to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.49,0:23:31.07,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,1)}Welcome to Sakura Hall
